{"id": "noos031", "name": "Cam_Butsudou_698_06_02", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Butsudou"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DoorButsudou", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "I said I would come back.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>Mr. Huang. Greetings.\nYou have 20 seconds. Please ask your question.</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "... So you only bought 20 seconds? I didn't know that Hou Sang Tong is already this poor, Mr. Huang.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "20 seconds... are more than enough.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Button", "Flips switch"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "......!?\nUgh! Ark ark! Blarghhh!\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "Hahaha! Idiot! Did you really think that I can't do anything with a fake report?\nHave a taste of my masterpiece!\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mogura Bodyguard"], "content": "Boss!\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunFight", "Gunshot"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "image", "attrs": ["noos3101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mogura Bodyguard"], "content": "Arghhhh!\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>ROBO!</i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "... What... did you do...\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "A nano-capsule developed by Kim. The moment I flip this switch, the capsule will explode within your body and release The Ender virus... You're getting too old, Manson. Bet you didn't expect that I added some extra \"ingredients\" to your meal, didn't you?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["KickGun", "Kicks gun away"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "Without a gun, you're nothing more than a worthless hack. Karma's a b****, Manson. Enjoy your death from a \"cause\" you created on your own.\nAs with this little girl, I'll gladly take her. \"The Eye of Horus\" shall be property of the Hou Sang Tong. Muhahaha!\nGrab her!\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "No problemo!\n... Don't hate me, Nora. It's Phoenix who caused all of this. If you want to hate someone, hate him. Hehehe!\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Let me go! ROBO! Wake up!</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "It's useless. This baby here is armed with EMP Armor-piercing rounds! He is now nothing more than a pile of scrap metal, haha!\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "Consecutive Gunshots"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang", " Hou Sang Tong Bodyguard"], "content": "ARGHHHHH!\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "......!?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "Cough cough... As long as I'm alive... always remember... to kick the gun further away from me... cough cough... bunch of idiots...\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "... You!\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "Gunshot"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "Haha... Cough... Only you left... Put Nora down, and I'll grant you a less painful death... Cough cough...\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "... Impossible!? Why aren't you dead!?\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "I told you before... You're not even half as capable as Phoenix... He has developed a vaccine that can vastly reduce the power of The Ender a while ago. Furthermore, he went ahead and tested it on multiple key members of the organization already... If you increased the virus concentration in the capsule, maybe I'm already dead by now... For the first time in my life... I have to thank you for your foolishness...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "D... <font size=\"3.6\">Don't come near me! Another step and I'll blow her brains out!</font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "Did you forget... what happened to you the last time you utter those words?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "Loads Gun"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i><font size=\"3.6\">Detect...... Nora...... Danger......!!</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "!?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i><font size=\"3.6\">Detect...... Nora...... Danger......!!</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>ROBO! NO!</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Hit", "Heavy Blow"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "ARGH!\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Hit", "Heavy Blow"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "UGH!!\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i><font size=\"4.0\">STOP IT! [NORA] !!</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>... Creator... voiceprint command... verification... success.\nNora, goodbye...</i>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Off", "ROBO_Head Shutdown"], "content": ""}, {"id": 45, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_On", "ROBO_Head Start-Up"], "content": ""}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>This unit, start-up, success. Running self-diagnostics... complete.\nDetect multiple physical damages on hardware.</i>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>Analyzing situation... Unable to comprehend.</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Kill... ROBO... killed someone.</i>\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>... Everyone. here?</i>\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>No... Only uncle Lam and Kim... That's not the point. The Mogura people will discover this immediately... We need to run away, fast! Let's go back to Kyuu Hou Kai first! Phoenix is still there!</i>\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Butsudou"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DoorButsudou", "ドアが開く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "また来ると言っただろう。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>コウさん、こんにちは。\nあなたの時間は20秒です。\n質問をどうぞ。</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "……20秒だと？\n虎盛堂はそんなに金に困ってるのか？コウさんよ。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "20秒で……十分だ。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Button", "スイッチON"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "………！？\nッグ！ゴホッ！ぅあ…ぐあああ！\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "ははははは！バカが！\n偽のレポートで俺を騙せると思ったか？\n俺様の傑作を受けてみやがれ！\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["土竜護衛"], "content": "ボス！\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunFight", "銃声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "image", "attrs": ["noos3101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["土竜護衛"], "content": "うああああああ！！！！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>ROBO！</i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "お前……何を……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "キムの発明したナノカプセルだ。\nスイッチを押すだけで、お前らの体内で爆発し、終焉ウィルスが解放される仕組みになっている。\n……年を取ったな、マンソン。\n自分の食ってる飯の中に私がスパイスを仕込んでいるとは思わなかっただろう？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["KickGun", "銃を蹴る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "銃さえ手に取らなければ、ただの役立たずだ。\n因果応報、死ぬんだな。\nこの子供は私が引き取ろう。\n「ホルスの目」は、虎盛堂の物だ！ふはははは！\n連れて行け！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "はい！\n……俺を恨むなよ、Nora。\nPhoenixが事態をここまで悪化させたんだ。\n恨むなら、あいつを恨め。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>放して！ROBO！起きて！</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "無意味だ。\nこれはマルス弾だからな。\nあんなロボット、一瞬で鉄くずさ。ははははは！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連続した銃声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang、虎盛堂護衛"], "content": "うわあああ！！\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "………！？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "ゴホッゴホッ……次からはよく覚えておけよ……俺がいる時は……銃を俺から遠ざけるってな……ゴホッ……愚かなやつだ……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "……お前！\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "銃声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "はっ……ゲホッ……あとはお前だけだ……Noraを放せ。\n楽に逝かせてやるよ……ゴホッゴホッ……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "……なぜだ！なぜ死なない！？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "言ったはずだ……お前にはPhoenixの半分の能力も備わっていないと……\nあいつはとっくに終焉を大幅に抑制するワクチンを開発済みだ。\n一部の重役がすでにテストとして使ってる……\nもし、カプセル内のウィルス濃度がもっと高ければ、俺は死んでたかもな……\n人生で初めて……お前の無能加減に感謝したよ……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "く……<font size=\"3.6\">来るな！こいつの頭ぶち抜くぞ！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "前回、自分がそのセリフを言ったときのことを……もう忘れたか？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "銃を構える"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i><font size=\"3.6\">Noraの危険を……検知しました……！！</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "！？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i><font size=\"3.6\">Noraの危険を……検知しました……！！</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>ROBO！ダメ！</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Hit", "重撃"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "グハッ！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Hit", "重撃"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "グアア！！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i><font size=\"4.0\">止めて！「NORA」！！</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……製造者声紋……指令を……確認しました……Nora、おやすみなさい……</i>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Off", "ROBO_Head シャットダウン"], "content": ""}, {"id": 45, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_On", "ROBO_Head スタートアップ"], "content": ""}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>本機は正常に起動されています。自己診断中……完了しました。\nハードウェアに複数の物理的破損を確認しました。</i>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>状況分析中……分かりません。</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>殺しちゃった……ROBO……人を殺しちゃったの。</i>\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……ここの全員ですか？</i>\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>違う……\nラムおじさんとキム……\n重要なのはそこじゃなくて、土竜の人がすぐに気が付いてここに来るはず……\n早く逃げないと！\nとりあえず、玖凰會に帰ろう！\nPhoenixはまだあそこにいる！</i>\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Butsudou"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DoorButsudou", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "我說過我會再來的。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>黃先生。您好。\n您有 20 秒的時間，請提問。</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "……只買 20 秒？我不知道虎盛堂已經窮成這樣了啊，黃先生。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "20 秒……就夠了。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Button", "開關啟動"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "……！？\n嗚！咳咳！嗚噁啊啊啊！\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "哈哈哈！蠢蛋！你以為給我假的報告我就沒搞頭了嗎？\n吃老子的傑作吧！\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["土竜保鏢"], "content": "老大！\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunFight", "槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "image", "attrs": ["noos3101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["土竜保鏢"], "content": "呃啊啊啊！！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>ROBO！</i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "……你……做了什……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "是金發明的奈米膠囊，只要我按下開關，就會在你體內引爆，釋放終焉病毒……你老了啊，文生。沒想過自己吃的飯菜裡會被我加料吧？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["KickGun", "踢走槍枝"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "只要不能拿槍，你就跟廢物沒兩樣，你就死在自己吞下的「因果」中吧。\n這小女孩我帶走了，以後「荷魯斯之眼」將會是虎盛堂的東西，哼哼哼。\n把她帶走！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "沒問題！\n……別恨我啊，Nora。是 Phoenix 讓事情變成這樣的，去恨他吧，嘻嘻！\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>放開我！ROBO！快醒來！</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "沒用的，這是帶脈衝波的穿甲彈，那種破鐵皮一下就會被打成廢鐵，哈哈。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang、虎盛堂保鏢"], "content": "哇啊啊啊！\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "……！？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "咳咳……只要我還在……就記得……把槍踢遠點……咳咳……蠢材……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "……你！\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "哈……咳……剩你了……把 Nora 放下，我可以讓你死得輕鬆點……咳咳……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "……怎麼會！？你為什麼沒死！？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "我說過……你沒有 Phoenix 一半的能力……他早就開發出可以大幅抑制終焉的疫苗，先在幾個重要幹部身上測試了……如果你提高膠囊內病毒的濃度的話，也許我會死吧……我人生第一次……要感謝你的低能啊……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "別……<font size=\"3.6\">別過來！不然我一槍打爛她的頭！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "你忘記……自己上次說出這句台詞的下場了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "舉槍"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i><font size=\"3.6\">偵測到……Nora……危險……！！</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "！？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i><font size=\"3.6\">偵測到……Nora……危險……！！</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>ROBO！不要！</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Hit", "重擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "呃啊！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Hit", "重擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "唔啊！！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i><font size=\"4.0\">快住手！「NORA」！！</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……創造者……聲紋指令……核對……\nNora，再見……</i>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Off", "ROBO_Head 關機"], "content": ""}, {"id": 45, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_On", "ROBO_Head 啟動"], "content": ""}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>本機，已正常啟動，執行自我診斷……完成。\n偵測到硬體多處發生物理損傷。</i>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>分析狀況……理解不能。</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>殺了……ROBO……殺人了。</i>\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……這裡，全部的人？</i>\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>不……只有林叔跟金……這不是重點，土竜的人很快會發現……我們得快點逃走，先回玖凰會吧！Phoenix 還在那邊！</i>\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Butsudou"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DoorButsudou", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "내가 다시 올 거라고 말하지 않았나.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>황 선생, 안녕하세요.\n20초의 시간이 주어집니다. 질문을 시작해 주십시오.</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "......겨우 20초라고? 호성당이 언제 이렇게 빈털털이가 돼버린 걸까, 황 선생?\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "20초면...... 충분하다.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Button", "스위치 ON"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "......!?\n으윽! 크으윽! 크아아아아악!\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "하하하하하! 멍청한 놈! 내게 가짜 보고서를 주고도 내가 그냥 넘어갈 줄 알았나 보지? 이 몸의 걸작이나 맛보시지!\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["토룡 경호원"], "content": "형님!\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunFight", "총성"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "image", "attrs": ["noos3101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["토룡 경호원"], "content": "으아아아악!!\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>ROBO!</i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "...네 놈.... 대체 무엇을....\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "김이 발명한 나노 캡슐이다. 스위치를 눌러 전원을 키거나 끄기만 하면, 종언 바이러스가 해방된다.... 네놈 말이다, Manson. 네놈이 먹고 있던 밥에 다른 것들까지 집어넣었을 줄은 꿈에도 몰랐나 보지?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["KickGun", "총을 발로 차버린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "총을 쥐지 않은 네놈은 쓰레기와 다름없다. 그리고 네놈은 업보대로 이곳에서 죽게 될 것이다.\n이 아이는 내가 데려가겠다. 「호루스의 눈」의 눈은 이제 호성당의 것이다! 크하하하!\n저 아이를 데리고 가라!\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "문제없다!\n......날 너무 미워하지 말라고, Nora. 이건 모두 Phoenix 때문에 일어난 일이니, 그놈을 원망해라! 흐히히히히!\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>나를 놔 줘! ROBO! 어서 일어나!</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "소용없을 거다!\n이건 펄스파로 이루어진 철갑탄이거든! 쇳덩이로 이루어진 놈이  한 발이라도 맞게 되면 바로 고철 덩어리가 돼버리지! 크하하하!\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "총 연사"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang", " 호성당 경호원"], "content": "우아아아아아악!\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "......!?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "쿨럭 쿨럭.... 나를 확실하게 처리하려면... 총을 더 멀리 차버렸어야지... 쿨럭... 멍청한 놈들...\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": ".......네놈이!\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "총성"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "하아.... 쿨럭.... 네놈만 남았군.... Nora를 내려놔라. 그러면 고통 없이 편안하게 보내줄 테니... 쿨럭....\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "....어째서! 어째서 아직 살아있는 거냐!?\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "내가 말하지 않았나.... 네 녀석은 Phoenix의 능력의 반도 안 된다고..... 그 녀석은 이미 오래전에 종언 바이러스를 최대한 억제할 수 있는 항체를 만들어냈다. 그리고 우선적으로 조직의 중요 간부들을 임상 실험 대상으로 그 항체를 투여했다.... 만약 네놈이 캡슐 안에 있는 바이러스의 농도를 높일 생각을 했다면.... 난 이미 죽어버렸겠지.... 내 인생 처음으로.... 네놈의 멍청한 두뇌에 감사하다고 말하고 싶은 기분이야....\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "오.......<font size=\"3.6\">오지 마!! 안 그러면 이 아이의 머리통을 날려버릴 테니깐!!</font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "...예전에 네가 그 말을 하고 나서 어떻게 됐는지 벌써 까먹은 거냐...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "총을 장전한다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i><font size=\"3.6\">Nora를 위협하는 대상을…………감지했습니다.....!!</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "!?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i><font size=\"3.6\">Nora를 위협하는 대상을…………감지했습니다.....!!</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>ROBO! 안돼!!</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Hit", "펀치"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "크억!\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Hit", "펀치"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "우아아악!\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i><font size=\"4.0\">그만 멈춰! 「NORA」!!</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>......창조자의 성문 지령이....확인되었습니다......\nNora, 안녕히...</i>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Off", "ROBO_Head 시스템 종료"], "content": ""}, {"id": 45, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_On", "ROBO_Head 부팅"], "content": ""}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>본 기기가 정상적으로 부팅되었습니다. 자가진단을 실행합니다.... 자가진단 완료.\n하드웨어 곳곳에 물리적인 파손이 감지되었습니다.</i>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>상황 분석 중...... 파악 불가.</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>죽였어..... ROBO.... 사람을 죽였어.</i>\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>....이곳의 전원을 말입니까?</i>\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>아니.....\n여기 Lam아저씨랑 김을.... 지금 이런 얘기 할 때가 아니야! 토룡의 사람들이 금방 발견할 거야..... 우리는 빨리 도망쳐야 해....먼저 구황회로 가자! Phoenix가 아직 그곳에 있어!</i>\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Butsudou"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DoorButsudou", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "我說過我會再來的。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>黃先生。您好。\n您有 20 秒的時間，請提問。</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "……只買 20 秒？我不知道虎盛堂已經窮成這樣了啊，黃先生。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "20 秒……就夠了。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Button", "開關啟動"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "……！？\n嗚！咳咳！嗚噁啊啊啊！\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "哈哈哈！蠢蛋！你以為給我假的報告我就沒搞頭了嗎？\n吃老子的傑作吧！\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["土竜保鏢"], "content": "老大！\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunFight", "槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "image", "attrs": ["noos3101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["土竜保鏢"], "content": "呃啊啊啊！！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>ROBO！</i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "……你……做了什……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "是金發明的奈米膠囊，只要我按下開關，就會在你體內引爆，釋放終焉病毒……你老了啊，文生。沒想過自己吃的飯菜裡會被我加料吧？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["KickGun", "踢走槍枝"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "只要不能拿槍，你就跟廢物沒兩樣，你就死在自己吞下的「因果」中吧。\n這小女孩我帶走了，以後「荷魯斯之眼」將會是虎盛堂的東西，哼哼哼。\n把她帶走！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "沒問題！\n……別恨我啊，Nora。是 Phoenix 讓事情變成這樣的，去恨他吧，嘻嘻！\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>放開我！ROBO！快醒來！</i>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "沒用的，這是帶脈衝波的穿甲彈，那種破鐵皮一下就會被打成廢鐵，哈哈。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang、虎盛堂保鏢"], "content": "哇啊啊啊！\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "……！？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "咳咳……只要我還在……就記得……把槍踢遠點……咳咳……蠢材……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "……你！\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_02", "槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "哈……咳……剩你了……把 Nora 放下，我可以讓你死得輕鬆點……咳咳……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "……怎麼會！？你為什麼沒死！？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "我說過……你沒有 Phoenix 一半的能力……他早就開發出可以大幅抑制終焉的疫苗，先在幾個重要幹部身上測試了……如果你提高膠囊內病毒的濃度的話，也許我會死吧……我人生第一次……要感謝你的低能啊……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "別……<font size=\"3.6\">別過來！不然我一槍打爛她的頭！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "你忘記……自己上次說出這句台詞的下場了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "舉槍"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i><font size=\"3.6\">偵測到……Nora……危險……！！</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "！？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i><font size=\"3.6\">偵測到……Nora……危險……！！</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>ROBO！不要！</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Hit", "重擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "呃啊！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Hit", "重擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "唔啊！！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i><font size=\"4.0\">快住手！「NORA」！！</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……創造者……聲紋指令……核對……\nNora，再見……</i>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Off", "ROBO_Head 關機"], "content": ""}, {"id": 45, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_On", "ROBO_Head 啟動"], "content": ""}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>本機，已正常啟動，執行自我診斷……完成。\n偵測到硬體多處發生物理損傷。</i>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>分析狀況……理解不能。</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>殺了……ROBO……殺人了。</i>\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……這裡，全部的人？</i>\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>不……只有林叔跟金……這不是重點，土竜的人很快會發現……我們得快點逃走，先回玖凰會吧！Phoenix 還在那邊！</i>\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Butsudou"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DoorButsudou", "开门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "我说过我会再来的。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>黄先生。您好。\n您有 20 秒的时间，请提问。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "……只买 20 秒？我不知道虎盛堂已经穷成这样了啊，黄先生。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "20 秒……就够了。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Button", "开关启动"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "……！ ？\n呜！咳咳！呜恶啊啊啊！\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "哈哈哈！蠢蛋！你以为给我假的报告我就没搞头了吗？\n吃老子的杰作吧！\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["土竜保镖"], "content": "老大！\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunFight", "枪声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "image", "attrs": ["noos3101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["土竜保镖"], "content": "呃啊啊啊！ ！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>ROBO！ </i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "……你……做了什……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "是金发明的奈米胶囊，只要我按下开关，就会在你体内引爆，释放终焉病毒……你老了啊，文生。没想过自己吃的饭菜里会被我加料吧？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["KickGun", "踢走枪枝"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Huang"], "content": "只要不能拿枪，你就跟废物没两样，你就死在自己吞下的「因果」中吧。\n这小女孩我带走了，以后「荷鲁斯之眼」将会是虎盛堂的东西，哼哼哼。\n把她带走！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kim"], "content": "没问题！\n……别恨我啊，Nora。是 Phoenix 让事情变成这样的，去恨他吧，嘻嘻！\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversa